'''''Freedom of Sullust''''' was a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvette]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]]. In [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], ''Freedom of Sullust'' was part of a task force sent to the [[Kessel/Legends|Kesselian]] space surrounding [[Maw Cluster/Legends|the Maw]] to engage a pirate [[Skirmish near Kessel|raid]] on a spice transport. The [[Invids|Invid]] forces under the command of [[Shala]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] began taking losses, but were saved by the timely arrival of [[Leonia Tavira]] and ''[[Invidious]]''. In the subsequent battle, ''Freedom of Sullust'' took heavy damage from ''Invidious''{{'}} guns and was driven from the fight.

